00:51:23,039 --> 00:51:24,332
It's acquisition.
这是一种攫取

553
00:51:24,708 --> 00:51:26,835
Carlisle might not ask you to fight, but I will.
卡莱尔或许不求你们战斗 但是我会

554
00:51:27,335 --> 00:51:30,172
